content: Fault in the game, have installed game several times and restarted and updated phone but every time try to play one of the games there is no sound. The planet's playing music there is no sound. Shame because rest of game is good.

A game about nothing but ironically it does work. Needs more to do. For toddlers only. Great for people ages 2 to 4 years of age. Any older and it will not hold children's interest from the lack of content and lack of brain stimulating activities. Aside that, it's great. Looks good too. Love the art style. Worth it's price.
Good app i loved the way you can make a dream for sarah and her friends. The same bread game its very good and its gets harder wich is good.
Love this game. Teaches fine motor skills and problem solving.

Crashes upon start-up. Contacted the developer twice with NO response whatsoever in a 2 week period. Very poor service. Won't be purchasing from this developer again. They take your money for a game that doesn't work and don't even respond when you request assistance. Disgusting
Excellent fun for my 2y/o daughter but WHY DOES IT WANT PERMISSION TO MAKE AND RECEIVE CALLS??  App developers: Explain why you want permissions or don't ask for them.  I'd give it 5 stars otherwise.

Paid for it. But does not work. Keeps saying looking for resources to download then the app won't open. Disappointed little girl. Email sent for support but no reply. Received new update for 'minor bug fixes' but still having same issue.
